      <title>Jupiter 的 Mark Nash 买入英国政府债券，押注英国央行将大幅降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/jupiter-s-nash-loads-up-on-gilts-in-wager-boe-will-slash-rates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[木星资产管理公司的马克·纳什抓住了英国政府债券收益率飙升的机会，大举购买英国政府债券，因为他预期英国央行将以超过市场目前预期的幅度降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/jupiter-s-nash-loads-up-on-gilts-in-wager-boe-will-slash-rates</guid>
